Developer Terms of Use
des:
kumparan is a leading digital news media platform and the first collaborative media platform in Indonesia with 80 million monthly audience.

Launched in 2017, kumparan incorporates journalism, storytelling, and technology in reporting (technology-based journalism). Founding partners and management of kumparan are widely recognised pioneers in Indonesian online media with over 15+ years of professional experience. 

kumparan committed to presenting innovative contents and products for Indonesian audiences. Content is provided in the Indonesian language. 

www.kumparan.com
